        <cb:mulu level="1" type="分"/>
        <cb:mulu level="2" type="經"/>
        <cb:div type="fen">
          <lb n="0011a02" ed="T"/>
          <milestone unit="juan" n="2"/>
          <lb n="0011a03" ed="T"/>
          <lb n="0011a04" ed="T"/>
          <cb:juan n="002" fun="open">
            <cb:mulu n="002" type="卷"/>
            <cb:jhead><title>佛說長阿含經</title>卷第二</cb:jhead>
          </cb:juan>
          <lb n="0011a05" ed="T"/>
          <lb n="0011a16" ed="T"/>
          <p>我。我欲伐之。不審世尊何所誡ka。若有
<lb n="0011a21" ed="T"/>阿闍世yā首佛足。敬問慇懃。起居輕利。遊步
<lb n="0011a24" ed="T"/>誡[(王*巨)/木]。</p>
          <lb/>
        </cb:div>
